title: Hellada Greek Tavern and Pizzeria
typeOfFood: Lacto, Pizza, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Greek, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Tavern with veg items including hummus, lentil soup, baked vegetables in tomato sauce, mixed salad with olives. A few dishes can be made vegan upon request including stuffed zucchini with rice, salad with beets & spinach and zucchini sticks.
